      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 09:27:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Burberry 更换首席执行官，暂停派息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-15/burberry-replaces-ceo-suspends-dividend-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Burberry Group Plc 周一暂停派息，并表示奢侈品行业销售放缓的趋势持续到了 7 月。该公司还更换了首席执行官。Jonathan Akeroyd 在这家英国公司任职不到两年半后即将离职，Joshua Schulman 将接替他的职位。彭博社的 Chloe Meley 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-15/burberry-replaces-ceo-suspends-dividend-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 09:26:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普攻击油价并关注中国经济数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普遭遇暗杀后，油价震荡上涨或下跌，而中国公布的经济数据更为疲弱，给北京方面带来更大压力，要求其在本周的重要政策会议上增强信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 23:29:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国期货上涨，10 年期收益率因特朗普押注而上升：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/us-futures-waver-as-traders-juggle-trump-win-bets-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在遭遇暗杀后，投资者加大对唐纳德·特朗普将赢得总统大选的押注，导致美国股指期货上涨，长期债券价格下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/us-futures-waver-as-traders-juggle-trump-win-bets-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 22:18:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
